{
  "name": "RPlog_Luke_and_the_Noghri",
  "title": "Luke and the Noghri",
  "summary": "Walking incognito through a busy district street, Jedi Master Luke Skywalker is stalked and ambushed by the hidden Noghri assassin Ahkaurakh, sent to test the man known as the Son of Vader. Luke effortlessly turns aside the assassin's gaderffi and blaster fire, refusing to fight in earnest, while nearby a band of street musicians, including the disguised redheaded girl Shenner and the watchful Grathix, scatters in alarm. As Ahkaurakh melts back into the shadows, a sinister voice reaches Luke through the Force, tormenting him with visions of Han Solo in agony and claiming Luke's destiny lies with its master. Drawn into a trance by the voice and dimly aware of Leia reaching out in worry, Luke is nearly seized again by the Noghri, who menaces Shenner before withdrawing when Luke snaps back to alertness. Reassured through their bond that Luke is coming home, he extinguishes his blade, gathers the frightened Shenner, and hurries her away from the dangerous street.",
